<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr gnade nehst
              <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und etlich brief gesant hat, die wir fürbas
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>frewnd<ex>en</ex></expan> gen <expan>Heylprunn<ex>en</ex></expan> schikten an der
            reichsstette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botten daselbs zu
              <expan>bring<ex>en</ex></expan> und verhörn zu lassen etc., also tun wir
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns
                <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnde, die zu <expan>Heylprunn<ex>en</ex></expan> warn,
            gesagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie sölich brief an der reichsstett
                <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> daselbs also bracht und
              <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hort</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lassen und daz der stett botten
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Brandemburg, daselbs ein antwurt darauf getan
                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> antwurt der
                <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der marggraf dem <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>durchlewchtigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
              <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>munden</ex></expan>
<expan>römisch<ex>er</ex></expan> und zu <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, meyne <expan>fürczubring<ex>en</ex></expan>, als er in
                <expan>genantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habe, so er schierist zu
              <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>künigl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>kom<ex>m</ex>e</expan>. Denn wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>exalta<ex>ci</ex><hi rend="sup">o<ex>n</ex>is</hi></expan> crucis.</ab>
</div>
